tables.table_schema:
CREATE TABLE SimulationParameters (
	simulation_id INT PRIMARY KEY,
	parameter_name VARCHAR(50),
	parameter_value FLOAT,
	constant_name VARCHAR(50),
	constant_value FLOAT
);

CREATE TABLE SimulationLogs (
  log_id INT PRIMARY KEY,
  simulation_id INT,
  log_message TEXT,
  log_timestamp TIMESTAMP,
  FOREIGN KEY (simulation_id) REFERENCES SimulationParameters(simulation_id)
);

CREATE TABLE SimulationConstants (
    id INT PRIMARY KEY,
    constant_name VARCHAR(50),
    constant_value FLOAT,
    constant_unit VARCHAR(10),
    constant_description TEXT
);
